<h1 style='font-size:20pt;color:#003366;margin:24px 0 12px;font-weight:bold'>L6 — Feuille de route de déploiement</h1>
<blockquote style='border-left:4px solid #003366;margin:16px 0;padding:10px 20px;background:#f5f8fc;font-style:italic;color:#333'>Volume consolidé · L6</blockquote>
